    SkillUsed -->|是，尚未讀取| ReadExpIndex["讀 experience/_index.json"]
    ReadExpIndex --> ExpFound{"找到 skill-id？"}
    ExpFound -->|是| LoadExp["載入 experience/skill-[id].md<br/>回覆註明已讀取經驗"]
    ExpFound -->|否| MarkMissing["記入 missing_experience_skills<br/>任務結束時主動詢問是否記錄"]
    LoadExp --> NextStep4
    MarkMissing --> NextStep4

    NextStep4(["進入 Step 4：知識庫檢索<br/>（見流程圖二）"])

